: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;"> spreading Russian and Chinese propaganda</a>? On Twitter, he has <a hr=
ef=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29351707.292269/aHR0cHM=
6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9lbG9ubXVzay9zdGF0dXMvMTU3Njk2OTI1NTAzMTI5NjAwMA/607f07c=
eef4b8524a319a23cB0c7c4a52" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" =
target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important=
; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> endorsed most of Vladimir Putin=E2=80=
=99s war aims</a> in Ukraine, and in a lunch interview with the Financial T=
imes he <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29351707.2=
92269/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvNWVmMTQ5OTctOTgyZS00ZjAzLTg1NDgtY=
jVkNjcyMDI2MjNh/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBbc05a588" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" i=
